* Lester Smith (1904 – 1992), a British [[Doctor of Science|chemist]] ([[Fellow of the Royal Society|F.R.S.]]).{{sfn|Theosopedia}}
* Alexander Wilder (1823 – 1908), an American religious studies scholar and philosopher.{{sfn|Zirkoff|1966}}{{sfn|Сенкевич|2012|p=391}}
